{"tid":1930901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：不滿中國指美軍投毒 堅持「中國病毒」說法正確","createTime":"2020-03-18T01:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T01:44:04.000Z","uid":297045,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe30869a362925a90dc2bda0d1578b96a0d91b6","tid":1930901,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【武漢肺炎】特朗普堅持「中國病毒」準確：是中國想污名化美軍</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普日前在 Twitter 發帖，稱新型冠狀病毒是「中國病毒」(Chinese Virus)，引發外交風波，特朗普出席白宮記者會時再被問及此事，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他堅持自己無錯，又說是因為中國歧圖抹黑美軍把病毒傳開，才會反唇相稽。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，自己不滿中國指美國軍方把病毒傳開，因為這不是事實：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國在散播不實言論，捏造事實。與其爭論，不如直接說出病毒源頭，病毒的確是源自中國，所以我認為這說法（「中國病毒」）非常準確。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n被問到用「中國病毒」想有污名化之嫌，特朗普否認，又說：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「說美軍把病毒傳開去才是污名化。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%BA%96%E7%A2%BA-%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%83%B3%E6%B1%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%8C%96%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D/?fbclid=IwAR3vK1mZe2d1KsjFrVKC2zS9ehz0VDvPucGeO0jwGnQJWLXE1ep4_lUgDLk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%25BA%2596%25E7%25A2%25BA-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2583%25B3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3vK1mZe2d1KsjFrVKC2zS9ehz0VDvPucGeO0jwGnQJWLXE1ep4_lUgDLk&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=1020bc38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F